```{r pancreas 32418758, include=FALSE}

PMID_32418758 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32418758', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32418758 <- paste0(PMID_32418758$journal,' ', PMID_32418758$year, ' ', PMID_32418758$month,';', PMID_32418758$volume,'(', PMID_32418758$number,'):', PMID_32418758$pages)

PubMed_32418758 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32418758$eprint)

doi_32418758 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32418758$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
